Typo Top Commenters Sidebar
===========================

Typo Top Commenters Sidebar displays your top commenters on your Typo blog sidebar. Sounds obvious no? Default number is 10, but this can be changed in your admin. 


Install
=======

Installing Typo Top Commenters Sidebar is easy. 

Go to your Typo blog directory and run

./script/plugin install git://github.com/fdv/topcomments_sidebar.git

Then, restart your Typo blog, go to your admin to enable to plugin into your sidebar.

If you don't have shell access to your Typo blog, you'll have to download the source and upload them using, for example, a FTP client.


